        `cminx`, `cminy`, `cmaxx`, `cmaxy` - The clipping rectangle.
        `reverse` - The transform from render to screen coordinates.
        `x`, `y` - The offset of the upper-left corner of the render.
        `focuses` - The list of focuses to add to.
